descriptionHtml:
[color=#f6b26b][b][center]Anastasia has gotten quite a few requests to become a preset, so I thought I would go ahead and upload her.

I have decided to include 2 different versions, one with [i][color=#5B0F00]brown[/color][/i] hair and one with [i][color=#8e7cc3]purple[/color].[/i][/center][/b][/color]

[size=4][i][b][center][color=#ff7700]*I have now also added a face sculpt file of her*[/color][/center][/b][/i][/size]

[center][color=#fce5cd][size=4]ENB's Used[/size][/color]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41470/?]First Seed ENB[/url] with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70451/?]Snapdragon ENB's DOF[/url][/center]

[center][url=https://flic.kr/p/Cqjfg7][img]https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1678/23903999540_164e54258f_c.jpg[/img][/url][/center]

[center][size=4][color=#ff0000]Requirements:[/color][/size]

[size=4][i][color=#ffe599](For her to look the same)[/color][/i][/size][/center]

[center][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url]

Spring's Kiss skin 2.0 by Faeofthewood [b][u][i][color=#93c47d]or[/color][/i][/u][/b][color=#93c47d] [/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36425/?]Real Girls[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup for SKSE[/url] (I use the High Res Female Face Makeup for SKSE)

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?]Seductive Lips[/url][/center]

[center][size=4][color=#dbb0a7]*Make sure to take a look at these mods descriptions as well*[/color][/size][/center]

[size=4]
[center][color=#ff0000]Manual Installation[/color][/center][/size]
[center]1. Download the Preset
2. Extract the file to a place of your choosing (I usually do desktop)
3. Put the file in Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets
4. Once in the game, start a new game or type in "showracemenu"
5. Set race to [i][color=#ffd966]Breton[/color][/i] and make sure you are on female
6. Then go to the Preset tab next to the tab that says sliders, and hit F9 and look for my preset
7. Click it, it should load, and she should be good to go[/center]


[color=#ff0000][center][size=4][b]Manual Uninstallation[/b][/size][/center][/color]
[center]1. Go to Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets and then remove my preset[/center]

[center][url=https://flic.kr/p/BUVCLS][img]https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1555/23571409314_fb88008ef1_c.jpg[/img][/url][/center]



[center][color=#ffd966][size=4]Credits[/size][/color]
Credit goes to all the authors of the mods that I mentioned above, without your guy's work, Anastasia, wouldn't have been possible to create[/center]
